| Go | `go test ./...` |

## Pass criteria

- All tests pass.
- Test count >= baseline (`.harness/scripts/baseline.json`).

## Coverage (if configured)

Coverage delta is informational. **Coverage decrease is a WARN, not a FAIL.**
But if coverage decrease coincides with a feature addition, investigate.

## Flake handling

Same as fullstack: 9/10 = flake = MAJOR defect.
